'''伯福德'''（[[英文|英文]]：Burford）位於英格蘭[[牛津郡|牛津郡]]西部[[科茨沃爾德丘陵|科茨沃爾德丘陵]][[溫德拉什河|溫德拉什河]]附近的一個小鎮，離[[牛津|牛津市]]以西約18英里（29公里），[[切爾滕納姆|切爾滕納姆]]東南面約22英里（35公里），以及格洛斯特郡邊界只有2英里（3公里）。該地名由來源於[[古英語|古英語]]單詞burh，意思解作設防城市或山城，以及穿越河流的淺灘。 2011年的人口普查記錄伯福德教區的人口為1410<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11121417&c=Burford&d=16&e=62&g=6459904&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1418412232234&enc=1 |title=Area: Burford (Parish): Key Figures for 2011 Census: Key Statistics |work=Neighbourhood Statistics |publisher=[[Office_for_National_Statistics|Office for National Statistics]] |accessdate=12 December 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003705/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11121417&c=Burford&d=16&e=62&g=6459904&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1418412232234&enc=1 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，以及伯福德區為1847<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=13694213&c=Burford&d=14&e=62&g=6459904&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1418412690345&enc=1 |title=Area: Burford (Ward): Key Figures for 2011 Census: Key Statistics |work=Neighbourhood Statistics |publisher=[[Office_for_National_Statistics|Office for National Statistics]] |accessdate=12 December 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081926/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=13694213&c=Burford&d=14&e=62&g=6459904&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1418412690345&enc=1 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

